{
  "id": "adv_event_2302_01_03",
  "title": "瑠依ちゃんの\n唇守り隊",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――レッスン終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the lesson",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "さあさあ瑠依ちゃ～ん\n二人でいーっぱい、キス……の練習しましょ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ Rui-chan~\nLet's practice… lots of kisses together~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0666666667,
      "endTime": 9.714254863299999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、さっきからベタベタし過ぎじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ isn't this getting too sticky all of a sudden?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9333333333,
      "endTime": 13.5937642892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "何言うてんの、キスはそこに至るまでの雰囲気も大事\nこれはその準備運動やんか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? The atmosphere leading up to a kiss is important too.\nThis is like a warm-up exercise~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8,
      "endTime": 21.457416793900002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "キスって、そういうものなんだ……\n優ちゃん、意外と大人だな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ a kiss is like that…\nYu-chan‚ you're surprisingly mature~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6666666667,
      "endTime": 28.720169570499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんも、もう一つ二つ大きなって\nこの人！　って人に出会えたら、分かると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ you'll grow up little by little too\nand when you meet that special someone‚ you'll understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9,
      "endTime": 35.687380827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれに妙なこと教え込まないの、まったく……\nでも……なるほど、参考になるわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't teach strange things to Sumire-chan‚ seriously…\nbut… I see‚ it's quite helpful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9,
      "endTime": 44.567612314200005,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8933.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依、着替え終わったか？\nそしたら次の現場に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ are you done changing?\nThen we should head to the next location…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6666666667,
      "endTime": 49.325892588,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9166.666666599995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、はい、{user}さん\nそれじゃあ二人とも、また後で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ yes‚ {user}-san.\nWell then‚ see you both later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5333333333,
      "endTime": 54.349465087599995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "はいは～い\n……瑠依ちゃん、ちょっと照れとって可愛かったな～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes yes~\n…Rui-chan was a bit shy and cute‚ wasn't she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0666666667,
      "endTime": 61.8472033501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私に同意を求められても……\nまぁでも、練習相手が優ちゃんなら安心……あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ even if you seek my agreement…\nif Yu-chan is my practice partner‚ I feel relieved… huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0666666667,
      "endTime": 71.7236949402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "結局本番は、俳優さんが相手のままだよね？\nそれだと結果は変わらないような……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But in the end‚ during the actual performance‚ it'll still be the actor‚ right?\nIn that case‚ outcome will remain the same…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2,
      "endTime": 79.3912925737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5666666667,
      "endTime": 81.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9,
      "endTime": 82.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "しまったあああ……！！\n結局、瑠依ちゃんの唇は奪われてまううう！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my god…!!\nIn the end‚ Rui-chan's lips will be stolen!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333333333,
      "endTime": 89.2526636979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "完全に……盲点やった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Completely… unexpected…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4666666667,
      "endTime": 93.49807264009999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "今日の優ちゃん、ものすごーくポンコツだけど……\n……本当に大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan today is incredibly clumsy‚ but…\n…Are you really okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9,
      "endTime": 100.9279826155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱあかん\n今回のお仕事、このまま進めるんは許されへん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ I can't allow this.\nWe can't proceed with this job as it is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1333333333,
      "endTime": 107.4698864301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "こうなったらうちが！　なんとしてでも！！\n瑠依ちゃんのキスを阻止したる！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ I will do anything to prevent it!!\nI will stop Rui-chan's kiss by any means necessary!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7,
      "endTime": 113.5992529646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "今ここに！　うちは！！\n『瑠依ちゃんの唇守り隊』結成を宣言しますっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right here‚ right now‚ we declare!!\nThe formation of the \"Lip Protection Squad for Rui-chan\"!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8,
      "endTime": 120.208246519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんの唇……守り隊？\nそれ、何するの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan's lips… protection squad?\nWhat's that for?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4333333333,
      "endTime": 126.0606392996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ……善は急げって言いますし\nすみれちゃんにもさっそく見せてあげます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… they say haste makes waste.\nI'll show Sumire-chan right away too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2666666667,
      "endTime": 133.8144143001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ優ちゃん、こんな所で何するの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Yu-chan‚ what are you doing here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1,
      "endTime": 140.3155101776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……これです！\nてってれ～、恋のおまじないセット～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… See this!\nTa-da! A love spell set~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5,
      "endTime": 147.9830077126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "て、てってれ〜？　……というか、え？\nそれ、どこからどう見てもわら人形……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-Ta-da? …I mean‚ huh?\nThat's a straw doll no matter how you look at it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1666666667,
      "endTime": 157.0085713705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "何言うてるん、恋のおまじないセットです\nうちと瑠依ちゃんの関係を邪魔する俳優さんを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? It's a love charm set.\nWe'll use this doll to curse the actor who's getting in the way of me and Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.2333333333,
      "endTime": 165.26224379090002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 165.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "この人形使って地獄に落としてしまえば\n晴れてうちらは……ふふ、ふふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once we send him to hell with this doll‚\nwe'll be able to…happily… hehe‚ hehehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.4666666667,
      "endTime": 175.29627269570003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 175.6333312988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
